---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import portrait from '../assets/christian_sisti.jpg';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Engineering Director with 15+ years of experience scaling global engineering organizations and modernizing high-traffic platforms."
>
  <div class="py-4">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-navy-500 mb-3">About</p>
    <Image
      src={portrait}
      alt="Christian Sisti"
      width={192}
      height={192}
      class="rounded-full object-cover mb-5 ring-2 ring-warm-100 w-24 h-24"
    />
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-navy-950 mb-2">Christian Sisti</h1>
    <p class="text-navy-500 text-lg mb-10">
      High-Energy, Customer-Centered, Flow-Driven Engineering Director
    </p>

    <hr class="border-warm-100 mb-10" />

    <!-- Bio -->
    <div class="space-y-6 text-navy-700 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Delivery-oriented Engineering Director with over <strong class="font-medium text-navy-900">15 years of experience</strong> in
        the technology sector, specializing in scaling global engineering organizations
        and modernizing high-traffic platforms.
      </p>

      <p>
        I bridge the gap between complex technical strategy and business-critical KPIs.
        With a foundation in Human-Computer Interaction
        (<strong class="font-medium text-navy-900">Master's in CS, University of Pisa</strong>),
        I bring a researcher's analytical rigor to executive leadership.
      </p>

      <p>
        As Engineering Director at
        <strong class="font-medium text-navy-900">Ocado Technology</strong>,
        I used to oversee the critical pillars of the E-commerce Platform: Reliability, Performance,
        and Developer Experience. My focus was on creating "Platform Teams" (following
        Team Topologies) that empower stream-aligned teams to ship at velocity.
      </p>

      <p>
        I am deeply committed to the <strong class="font-medium text-navy-900">LeadDev</strong> philosophy.
        As a founding organizer in Barcelona, I curate spaces for engineering leaders to solve
        the industry's toughest organizational challenges. I don't just lead teams — I build
        the environments where technical excellence thrives.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-12 text-sm text-navy-500 italic">
      Highly skilled table soccer player&thinsp;;)
    </p>

  </div>
</Layout>
